org.perfidix.element

Class SequentialMethodArrangement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfidix.element.AbstractMethodArrangement
      • org.perfidix.element.SequentialMethodArrangement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<BenchmarkElement>

    public final class SequentialMethodArrangement
extends AbstractMethodArrangement
    This class represents an arrangement where each method is executed after another. That means that
    @Bench(runs=3) public bench1(){ .. }
    @Bench(runs=2) public bench2(){ .. }
    @Bench(runs=1) public bench3(){ .. }

    results in the following execution order:
    bench1 bench2 bench3 bench1 bench2 bench1
